A high quality development offering air-conditioning and carpeted office/showroom area and clearspan warehouses towards the rear of the tenancy.

The warehouse area is accessed via a container height roller door. The complex also has ISDN installed and is accessible to all tenancies.

•	280sqm tenancy within tightly held Albion
•	210sqm open plan showroom / warehouse 
•	70sqm high quality air-conditioned office space
•	Bonus 80sqm exclusive use area down the side of the building
•	Onsite car parking
•	Dual roller door access (front and side)
•	Prominent location opposite National Cricket Centre
•	Flexible space suitable to a variety of users

For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact Exclusive Marketing Agents CBRE.

Small office/warehouse located on the corner of Corunna and Moore Streets, Albion. The property is in close proximity to the pending redevelopment of the Albion Railway Station and enjoys the benefits of all forms of public transport.

Excellent complex with ample car parking on site.

* 661sqm freestanding office/showroom/warehouse
* 146sqm office/showroom
* 400sqm medium height warehouse with dual roller door access
* 115sqm standalone storage shed/workshop at rear of site
* 1,882sqm corner site with great exposure to passing traffic
* Unbeatable onsite car parking
* Suitable for a multitude of users
* Central location with easy access to main arterial & public transport options.

For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact Exclusive Agents CBRE.

* Freestanding Building with Exposure
* Warehouse with Roller Door Access
* Quality Air-Conditioned Office
* Option to Secure 200 sqm - 384 sqm
